0Scan.%3Cp%3EMaple%20Scan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20first%20hear%20about%20the%20app%2C%20they%20think%20it%20will%20just%20tell%20them%20whether%20something%20is%20Canadian%20or%20not%20and%20recommend%20an%20alternative.%20But%20our%20approach%20is%20different%20because%20that%20question%20is%20nuanced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20download%20the%20free%20app%2C%20you%20can%20take%20a%20photo%20of%20any%20product%20with%20the%20in-app%20camera.%20The%20AI-powered%20image%20recognition%20in%20the%20app%20will%20then%20read%20the%20label%20and%20search%20for%20information%20online%20and%20in%20our%20database%2C%20but%20it%20won't%20make%20a%20final%20judgment%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanada-turn-local-products-trump-tariffs-mislabeling-complaints-surge-fraud-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhether%20a%20product%20is%20Canadian%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20it%20will%20tell%20you%20about%20the%20ingredients%2C%20ownership%2C%20where%20it's%20manufactured%2C%20and%20how%20many%20people%20are%20employed%20there.%20The%20app%20surfaces%20all%20those%20different%20pieces%20of%20information%20so%20you%20can%20make%20a%20decision%20on%20your%20own.%20We%20don't%20want%20to%20make%20that%20judgment%20for%20you%20%E2%80%94%20we%20just%20want%20people%20to%20be%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20app%20can%20distinguish%20between%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanadian-stores-labeling-american-imports-consumers-responding-patriotism-trump-tariffs-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMade%20in%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BProduct%20of%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20are%20two%20different%20things%20based%20on%20how%20many%20of%20the%20ingredients%20come%20from%20here.%20It%20also%20includes%20ownership%20information%2C%20like%20whether%20it's%20a%20Canadian-owned%20brand%20or%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20a%20foreign%20company.%20It's%20about%20giving%20context%2C%20not%20just%20a%20label.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cfa01e41-1e41-4460-a036-536f28a897d6%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20community%20around%20conscious%20purchasing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222548%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Number%20of%20downloads%20and%20where%20the%20users%20are.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6882b1413d5881a51c1df773%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22838%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaple%20Scan%20has%20been%20downloaded%20more%20than%20110%2C000%20times%20since%20launching%20in%20March.%3Cp%3EMaple%20Scan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHonestly%2C%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20parts%20of%20this%20whole%20journey%20has%20been%20the%20community%20that's%20grown%20around%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaple%20Scan%20started%20as%20a%20solo%20project%2C%20but%20the%20support%20that%20came%20in%20almost%20immediately%20was%20beautiful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUniversity%20colleagues%2C%20people%20across%20Canada%2C%20and%20even%20total%20strangers%20reached%20out%20and%20said%20they%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ewanted%20to%20help%20with%20this%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20we%20have%20a%20group%20of%20volunteers%20with%20expertise%20in%20everything%20from%20social%20media%20marketing%20to%20food%20industry%20regulations%2C%20as%20well%20as%20mentorship%2C%20engineering%20support%2C%20and%20networking%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20support%20has%20been%20absolutely%20crucial%20to%20the%20app's%20growth.%20For%20example%2C%20people%20in%20the%20food%20industry%20have%20helped%20explain%20how%20long%20it%20takes%20for%20packaging%20to%20reflect%20a%20product's%20sourcing%2C%20sometimes%20months.%20So%2C%20when%20a%20company%20might%20not%20have%20a%20%26quot%3BMade%20in%20Canada%26quot%3B%20label%20yet%20but%20actually%20does%20source%20from%20Canada%2C%20Maple%20Scan%20can%20help%20bridge%20that%20gap%20and%20surface%20that%20informa