0the%20drink.%20Though%2C%20the%20%2479%20price%20tag%20for%20a%20six-pack%20is%20not%20as%20wallet-friendly%20as%20the%20regular%20version%20you'd%20find%20at%20a%20local%20dive%20or%20the%20one%20you%20could%20concoct%20in%20your%20kitchen.%20Given%20that%20an%20Aperol%20spritz%20could%20easily%20run%20you%20%2415%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20knock-off%20beer%20version%20is%20part%20of%20the%20draw.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSparkling%20wine%20comes%20with%20that%20assumed%20price%20tag%20because%20it%20doesn't%20really%20matter%20what%20people%20are%20paying%20for%20it%20on%20the%20backend%3B%20they're%20still%20going%20to%20charge%20you%20a%20fair%20amount%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Tom%20Brander%2C%20the%20beverage%20director%20at%20Wilder%2C%20a%20restaurant%20in%20Philadelphia.%20%26quot%3BAt%20a%20dive%20bar%2C%20you%20can%20just%20get%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20Aperol.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20origin%20of%20the%20Spaghett%20can%20be%20traced%20back%20to%20Wet%20City%20Brewing%20in%20Baltimore%20in%20the%20mid-2010s%2C%20where%20a%20bartender%20created%20it%20as%20a%20sort%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdepauliaonline.com%2F55300%2Fartslife%2Fspagett-a-cheap-regional-crowd-pleasing-cocktail%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebastardized%20Aperol%20spritz%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20Part%20of%20the%20Spaghett's%20allure%20has%20been%20that%20it's%20familiar%20to%20those%20who%20work%20in%20bars%20and%20restaurants.%20It's%20sort%20of%20a%20secret%20menu%20item.%20Stuart%20Wellington%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20Hinterlands%2C%20Minnie's%2C%20and%20Commonwealth%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20jokes%20it's%20a%20drink%20for%20%26quot%3Bservice%20industry%20nerds%20and%20other%20weirdos%20that%20are%20in%20the%20know.%26quot%3B%20It%20trickled%20out%20across%20the%20city%2C%20region%2C%20and%20eventually%20the%20country%20from%20there%2C%20getting%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bonappetit.com%2Fstory%2Fwet-city-brewing-spaghett%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBon%20App%C3%A9tit%3C%2Fa%3E%20writeup%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20could%20have%20foreseen%20that%20this%20silly%20little%20one-off%20cocktail%20would%20be%20this%20big%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Alexander%20Rudy%2C%20a%20bartender%20in%20Austin%20who%20used%20to%20live%20in%20Baltimore.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20like%20an%20industry%20handshake.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacquelyn%20Caldwell%2C%20an%20associate%20brand%20marketing%20manager%20for%20Miller%20High%20Life%2C%20says%20the%20brand%20has%20seen%20the%20Spaghett%20gain%20%26quot%3Bsteady%20momentum%2C%26quot%3B%20especially%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20%26quot%3BIt%20started%20as%20a%20bartender%20favorite%20in%20dive%20bars%20%E2%80%94%20mixed%20directly%20in%20the%20High%20Life%20bottle%2C%20no%20frills%2C%20just%20great%20flavor.%20From%20there%2C%20it%20evolved%20from%20an%20under-the-radar%20pick%20to%20a%20popular%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20facets%20to%20the%20Spaghett's%20appeal.%20It's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcool-cocktails-that-are-actually-easy-to-make-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esimple%20to%20make%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20you%20crack%20open%20a%20beer%2C%20maybe%20pour%20a%20little%20out%20or%20drink%20one%20swig%2C%20and%20then%20just%20toss%20in%20a%20half%20a%20shot%20of%20Aperol.%20The%20aperitif%20adds%20complexity%20to%20a%20drink%20without%20a%20lot%20of%20effort.%20While%20it's%20typically%20created%20with%20a%20High%20Life%2C%20you%20can%20attempt%20it%20with%20other%20beers%2C%20too.%20One%20bartender%20tells%20me%20Aperol%20in%20a%20hazy%20IPA%20is%20%26quot%3Bfire.%26quot%3B%20The%20people%20serving%20them%20up%20also%20appreciate%20the%20simplicity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPricier%20drinks%20take%20time%20to%20assemble%2C%20so%20the%20ability%20to%20churn%20out%20a%20round%20of%20drinks%20quickly%2C%20even%20if%20they%20are%20less%20expensive%2C%20is%20important%20when%20it%20is%20busy%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Frederic%20Yarm%2C%20a%20bartender%20and%20writer%20in%20Boston.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20era%20of%20more%20people%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falcohol-spending-trends-gen-z-millennials-baby-boomers-surgeon-general-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewatching%20their%20alcohol%20intake%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Spaghett%20has%20a%20relatively%20low%20ABV%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhard-seltzer-canned-cocktail-high-abv-beer-alcohol-drinks-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompared%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20options%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20drink%20is%20a%20sort%20of%20orangey-pink%2C%20it%20plays%20into%20the%20bottled%20cocktail%20trend%2C%20and%20it's%20just%20kind%20of%20fun%20to%20say%20the%20word%20%26quot%3BSpaghett.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20popularity%20of%20the%20Aperol%20spritz%2C%20you%20can%20only%20have%20so%20many%20until%20you're%20ready%20to%20venture%20into%20the%20next%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Julianna%20McIntosh%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Join%20Jules%2C%20a%20cocktail%20blog%2C%20and%20the%20author%20of%20the%20book%20%26quot%3BPretty%20Simple%20Cocktails.%26quot%3B%20It's%20a%20lot%20of%20guys%20who%20drink%20Spaghetts%2C%20but%20it%20appeals%20to%20women%2C%20too.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20way%20easier%20way%20for%2C%20I%20would%20say%2C%20to%20get%20the%20female%20demographic%20into%20beer%2C%26quot%3B%20McIntosh%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChances%20are%2C%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20find%20a%20Spaghett%20on%20the%20menu%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-city-gaudy-gilded-age-restaurants-bars-wall-street-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-end%20cocktail%20bar%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20expensive%20restaurant.%20It's%20one%20you%20come%20across%20in%20dive%20bars%20and%20more%20middle-of-the-road%20establishments%2C%20if%20it's%20on%20the%20menu%20at%20all%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20time%2C%20you%20just%20have%20to%20ask%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mawuli%20Grant%20Agbefe%2C%20a%20substitute%20teacher%20and%20Spaghett%20fan%20in%20Chicago%2C%20first%20started%20ordering%20Spaghetts%2C%20he'd%20sometimes%20have%20to%20explain%20what%20it%20was%20to%20the%20bartender.%20But%20he's%20started%20to%20notice%20it%20pop%20up%20on%20menus%20over%20the%20past%20year%20or%20two.%20He%20likes%20the%20taste%2C%20and%20he%20thinks%20it's%20an%20especially%20good%20option%20when%20it's%20hot%20out.%20%26quot%3BBefore%20I%20got%20into%20the%20Spaghett%2C%20I%20liked%20the%20Miller%20High%20Life%20plain%2C%20but%20after%20a%20bunch%20of%20High%20Life%20over%20the%20years%2C%20you%20kind%20of%20want%20to%20gussy%20it%20up%20sometimes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20charm%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeer-combo-cocktails-recipes-2014-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeer%20cocktails%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20making%20something%20not%20special%20a%20little%20special.%20The%20other%20part%20of%20the%20equation%3A%20the%20price.%20Trading%20down%20from%20an%20Aperol%20spritz%20to%20a%20Spaghett%20usually%20puts%20a%20few%20bills%20back%20in%20your%20pocket%2C%20while%20swapping%20a%20regular%20beer%20for%20a%20Spaghett%20isn't%20going%20to%20break%20the%20bank%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20regular%20beer%20is%20cheap%20to%20begin%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWellington%2C%20the%20Brooklyn%20bar%20owner%2C%20calls%20Miller%20High%20Life%20his%20%26quot%3Brecession%20beer.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI've%20definitely%20noticed%20within%20a%20certain%20portion%20of%20my%2C%20let's%20say%2C%20moderately%20employed%20regulars%2C%20they%20went%20from%20drinking%20draft%20beer%20to%20switching%20over%20to%20just%20drinking%20High%20Lifes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20His%20average%20weekly%20order%20of%20High%20Life%20has%20gone%20up%20%26quot%3Bconsiderably%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20Wellington%20has%20a%20buddy%20who%20has%20a%20full%20Spaghett%20setup%20at%20home%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20premixed%20squeeze%20bottle%20of%20Aperol%20and%20lime%20juice.%20Though%20he%20felt%20like%20they%20really%20hit%20last%20summer%2C%20he%20still%20sees%20them%20around%20and%20orders%20them%20himself.%20The%20idea%20of%20turning%20a%20beer%20into%20a%20Spaghett%20%26quot%3Bhas%20a%20little%20bit%20of%2C%20'Oh%2C%20we're%20going%20something%20fun%20today%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20The%20Spaghett%20is%20also%20cheaper%20than%20the%20other%20bar%20insider's%20secret%20combo%20%E2%80%94%20a%20beer%20and%20a%20shot%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeer-combo-cocktails-recipes-2014-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFernet%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20consumers%20are%20looking%20to%20pull%20back%20a%20bit%20on%20spending%20and%20shift%20to%20lower%20ABV%20beverages%2C%20we've%20seen%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20popularity%20of%20beer%20cocktails%20%E2%80%94%20across%20restaurants%20on%20Square%2C%20orders%20for%20Spaghetts%20and%20other%20beer%20and%20spirit%20mixes%20have%20been%20increasing%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Ming-Tai%20Huh%2C%20the%20head%20of%20food%20and%20beverage%20at%20Square.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20ask%20bartenders%20how%20much%20they%20charge%20people%20for%20the%20Spaghett%2C%20particularly%20if%20it's%20not%20on%20the%20menu%2C%20most%20of%20them%20laugh.%20One%20says%20they'll%20add%20a%20dollar%20or%20two%20onto%20the%20price%20of%20the%20beer%20they%20use%20as%20the%20base.%20Another%20says%20they%20may%20double%20the%20price%20of%20the%20already-inexpensive%20beer%2C%20or%20add%20the%20Aperol%20on%20as%20a%20shot.%20Others%20admit%20it's%20a%20bit%20of%20an%20it-depends%20situation%20%E2%80%94%20they%20might%20just%20let%20the%20splash%20of%20Aperol%20go%20and%20charge%20only%20the%20beer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20are%20nervous%20about%20the%20economy%2C%20they%20start%20to%20look%20for%20ways%20to%20get%20more%20bang%20for%20their%20buck.%20They%20trade%20restaurant%20visits%20for%20meals%20at%20home.%20They%20switch%20international%20vacations%20for%20more%20local%20destinations.%20Alcohol%20can%20be%20a%20place%20where%20people%20do%20some%20amount%20of%20splurging%20%E2%80%94%20who%20among%20us%20has%20been%20at%20a%20bar%20and%20had%20a%20drink%20or%20two%20more%20than%20anticipated%3F%20But%20they%20also%20find%20ways%20to%20cut%20corners.%20They%20buy%20alcohol%20in%20smaller%20bottles%2C%20or%20they%20try%20to%20find%20options%20that%20still%20do%20the%20trick%2C%20inebriation-wise%2C%20without%20breaking%20the%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20really%20a%20beer%20gal%2C%20and%20until%20recently%2C%20I%20had%20not%20heard%20of%20the%20Spaghett.%20I%20did%20go%20try%20one%20at%20a%20local%20bar%2C%20and%20let's%20just%20say%20it's%20not%20for%20me.%20But%20it%20is%20for%20plenty%20of%20other%20people.%20When%20I%20mentioned%20it%20to%20a%20coworker%2C%20they%20sent%20me%20a%20picture%20of%20their%20pink-hued%20High%20Life%20from%20the%20Fourth%20of%20July%20weekend.%20At%20a%20work%20event%2C%20I%20brought%20Spaghetts%20up%20to%20a%20stranger%20in%20passing%2C%20and%20he%20raved%20about%20them%20%E2%80%94%20this%20summer%2C%20they're%20his%20main%20drink.%20And%20whatever%20your%20liquor%20proclivities%2C%20once%20you%20start%20to%20notice%20a%20beer%20cocktail%20in%20one%20place%2C%20you%20notice%20them%20everywhere%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Corona%20sunrise%2C%20the%20beermosa%2C%20the%20lagerita%2C%20the%20shandy.%20Beer%20companies%20are%20finding%20ways%20to%20zhuzh%20it%20up%20for%20price-conscious%20drinkers%20in%20other%20ways%2C%20too%2C%20and%20consumers%20are%20biting.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravis-kelce-jason-kelce-brothers-brand-tv-clothing-endorsements-podcast-2024-11%5C%2