0by%20a%20local%20tech%20founder%20named%20Jeff%20Glattstein%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Lena%20Franklin%2C%20a%20social%20worker%20and%20Yoga%20Magazine%20cover%20star%2C%20EAST%20promoted%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20healing%20and%20transformation%26quot%3B%20through%20a%20combination%20of%20plant%20medicine%2C%20meditation%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bvibrational%20sound%20therapy.%26quot%3B%20Similar%20facilities%20have%20been%20sprouting%20up%20across%20the%20country%2C%20part%20of%20an%20entrepreneurial%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrodosing-psilocybin-mushrooms-for-creativity-startups-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshroom%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20spurred%20by%20the%20growing%20movement%20to%20legalize%20psilocybin%20for%20use%20in%20therapeutic%20settings%2C%20and%20a%20belief%20that%20these%20drugs%20could%20be%20the%20future%20of%20mental%20health%20treatment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETim%20found%20his%20first%20trip%2C%20in%202022%2C%20life-altering.%20It%20helped%20him%20let%20go%20of%20his%20feelings%20of%20shame%20about%20his%20sexuality%20and%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeople-who-used-psychedelics-to-treat-ptsd-describe-trips-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eheal%20the%20trauma%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20a%20sexual%20assault%20he%20had%20suffered%20years%20earlier.%20%26quot%3BIt%20sounds%20trite%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20so%20connected%20to%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalls.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20this%20light%20burst%20out%20from%20me%20in%20the%20form%20of%20these%20rainbow%20bullets.%20They%20pushed%20the%20predator%20away.%20I%20felt%20bathed%20in%20this%20light%20and%20energy%20and%20power%20that%20was%20simply%20beyond%20my%20own%20agency%2C%20beyond%20my%20own%20personal%20narrative%2C%20and%20beyond%20my%20own%20body.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToward%20the%20end%20of%20the%20session%2C%20Tim%20looked%20over%20at%20Glattstein%2C%20who'd%20been%20facilitating%20the%20trip.%20In%20his%2060s%2C%20wearing%20a%20woven%20poncho%20and%20a%20dazzling%20array%20of%20giant%20turquoise%20rings%2C%20the%20older%20man%20struck%20Tim%20as%20a%20guru%2C%20a%20healer%20who%20could%20deliver%20him%20from%20his%20guilt%20and%20pain.%20Still%20experiencing%20the%20trip's%20euphoric%20afterglow%2C%20he%20dubbed%20Glattstein%20the%20Light%20Keeper.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20ready%20to%20latch%20on%20to%20a%20savior%20at%20that%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Tim%20recalls.%20(He%20and%20other%20trainees%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20that%20they%20be%20identified%20with%20pseudonyms%2C%20since%20they%20could%20suffer%20professional%20consequences%20for%20using%20illegal%20drugs%20outside%20a%20clinical%20setting.%20Glattstein%20declined%20to%20comment%20for%20this%20story.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20get%20a%20head%20start%20in%20the%20exciting%20new%20field%20of%20hallucinogenic%20healing%2C%20Tim%20paid%20%2425%2C000%20to%20enroll%20in%20EAST's%20signature%20offering%3A%20a%20six-month%20course%20to%20train%20students%20to%20serve%20as%20facilitators%20of%20psilocybin-assisted%20therapy.%20During%20the%20sessions%20%E2%80%94%20which%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eincluded%20weekend%20ceremonies%20in%20which%20trainees%20would%20take%20turns%20tripping%20on%20high%20doses%20of%20mushrooms%20%E2%80%94%20Tim%20developed%20what%20he%20called%20an%20%26quot%3Beternal%20bond%26quot%3B%20with%20his%20fellow%20students%20and%20EAST's%20staff.%20He%20imagined%20a%20future%20where%20they%20would%20all%20take%20care%20of%20one%20another's%20children.%20(%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20mushrooms%20talking%2C%20of%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHalfway%20through%20the%20training%2C%20Tim's%20personal%20life%20imploded%20when%20his%20boyfriend%20of%20four%20years%20broke%20up%20with%20him.%20In%20his%20fragile%20state%2C%20he%20told%20two%20EAST%20employees%20that%20he%20thought%20he%20should%20take%20the%20weekend%20off%20from%20taking%20mushrooms.%20But%20when%20Glattstein%20handed%20him%20a%20high%20dose%2C%20Tim%20says%2C%20he%20took%20it.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20always%20this%20feeling%20that%20they%20must%20know%20something%20I%20don't%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223750%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20illustrated%20scene%20of%20a%20figure%20in%20a%20yoga%20pose%20surrounded%20by%20shadowy%20figures%20in%20front%20of%20a%20sun%20mural%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6824adf068a29290080147de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECenters%20for%20psychedelic%20medicine%2C%20part%20of%20an%20entrepreneurial%20shroom%20boom%2C%20have%20been%20sprouting%20up%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20market%20for%20psychedelic%20medicine%20could%20hit%20%2410%20billion%20by%202028.%3Cp%3EDeena%20So%20Oteh%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20night%2C%20and%20while%20he%20was%20still%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20the%20mushrooms%2C%20Tim%20says%20he%20was%20sexually%20assaulted%20by%20Scott%2C%20an%20EAST%20staff%20member%20responsible%20for%20ensuring%20that%20trainees%20got%20home%20safely%20from%20the%20ceremony.%20(Business%20Insider%20is%20referring%20to%20him%20by%20a%20pseudonym%3B%20he%20was%20never%20criminally%20charged.%20He%20denies%20Tim's%20allegation.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETim%20says%20he%20hoped%20to%20work%20with%20EAST%20to%20develop%20an%20ethics%20policy%20and%20roll%20out%20better%20safeguards.%20He%20set%20up%20a%20Zoom%20meeting%20with%20Glattstein%20and%20Franklin%2C%20and%20asked%20two%20of%20his%20closest%20confidants%20in%20the%20training%20council%2C%20Beth%20and%20Lisa%2C%20to%20join%20the%20call.%20%26quot%3BI%20knew%20I%20had%20been%20taken%20advantage%20of%20by%20someone%20who%20was%20supposed%20to%20take%20care%20of%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Tim.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20very%20concerned%20with%20ensuring%20something%20like%20this%20didn't%20happen%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20according%20to%20an%20audio%20recording%20of%20the%20meeting%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20the%20two%20founders%20said%20they%20%26quot%3Bbelieved%26quot%3B%20Tim.%20But%20when%20Beth%20suggested%20that%20the%20incident%20represented%20an%20institutional%20failure%20at%20EAST%2C%20Glattstein%20jumped%20in.%20%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20EAST%20being%20culpable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20had%20a%20person%20on%20our%20staff%20who%20stepped%20over%20the%20line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlattstein%20and%20Franklin%20hired%20a%20law%20firm%20to%20conduct%20an%20independent%20investigation%2C%20and%20Scott%20was%20ultimately%20fired.%20Franklin%20declined%20to%20share%20the%20resulting%20report%20with%20Business%20Insider.%20But%20in%20an%20email%20to%20the%20council%2C%20she%20wrote%20that%20the%20report%20concluded%20that%20EAST%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20culpability%20in%20the%20alleged%20events.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20things%20at%20EAST%20were%20about%20to%20get%20even%20more%20complicated%2C%20as%20multiple%20women%20came%20forward%20to%20accuse%20Glattstein%20of%20touching%20them%20inappropriately%20during%20healing%20sessions%20%E2%80%94%20accusations%20he%20denies.%20And%20such%20accusations%20aren't%20isolated%20to%20EAST.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20as%20drugs%20like%20MDMA%20and%20mushrooms%20have%20turned%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-compass-pathways-psychedelic-psilocybin-origin-story-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elucrative%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20accusations%20of%20abuse%20have%20begun%20to%20surface%20at%20a%20host%20of%20leading%20centers%20for%20psychedelic%20medicine.%20In%20the%20wake%20of%20decriminalizing%20psilocybin%2C%20cities%20and%20states%20have%20implemented%20few%20ground%20rules%20to%20govern%20the%20sudden%20explosion%20of%20%26quot%3Bconsciousness%20medicine.%26quot%3B%20And%20the%20same%20properties%20that%20make%20mushrooms%20so%20effective%20in%20repelling%20destructive%20thoughts%20can%20also%20render%20users%20highly%20suggestible%2C%20making%20them%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20cultlike%20dynamic%20that%20has%20long%20pervaded%20the%20world%20of%20psychedelic%20healing.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20people%20who%20have%20signed%20up%20to%20get%20care%20or%20serve%20as%20caregivers%20in%20the%20budding%20new%20industry%20say%20they've%20been%20harmed%20while%20taking%20the%20very%20drugs%20whose%20healing%20powers%20they%20were%20being%20taught%20to%20harness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20new%20field%2C%20and%20there%20are%20no%20real%20regulations%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedicalethicshealthpolicy.med.upenn.edu%2Ffaculty-all%2Fdominic-sisti%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDominic%20Sisti%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20medical%20ethics%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%20who%20has%20researched%20the%20ethical%20dilemmas%20involved%20in%20psychedelics.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20sort%20of%20the%20Wild%20West%20phenomenon%20where%20the%20most%20kind%20of%20aggressive%2C%20entrepreneurial%20people%20can%20take%20advantage%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EHumans%20have%20been%20getting%20high%20on%20magic%20mushrooms%20for%20almost%20as%20long%20as%20there%20have%20been%20humans.%20Popularized%20in%20the%20United%20States%20during%20the%201960s%2C%20psychedelics%20came%20under%20fire%20during%20the%20Nixon%20administration's%20%26quot%3Bwar%20on%20drugs.%26quot%3B%20In%201970%2C%20they%20were%20classified%20as%20Schedule%201%20substances%2C%20rendering%20possession%20illegal%2C%20even%20for%20research%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20in%202000%2C%20scientists%20at%20Johns%20Hopkins%20University%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ereceived%20permission%3Cspan%3E%20from%20the%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20to%20conduct%20research%20into%20psilocybin.%20As%20studies%20began%20to%20show%20that%20the%20substance%20had%20significant%20benefits%20for%20patients%20with%20chronic%20mental%20illness%2C%20voters%20started%20to%20see%20it%20more%20as%20medicine%20than%20menace.%20From%20Burning%20Man%20to%20luxury%20retreats%2C%20experimenting%20with%20psychedelics%20has%20become%20common%20among%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrodosing-psychedelics-entrepreneurs-founders-new-business-ideas-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etech%20founders%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20executives%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-psychedelics-burning-man-journeys-mdma-mushrooms-report-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sam-altman-psychedelics-helped-anxiety-happiness-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20who%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceos-founders-who-used-psychedelics-lsd-acid-magic-mushrooms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecredit%20the%20drugs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20quieting%20their%20nerves%2C%20boosting%20productivity%2C%20and%20allowing%20them%20to%20better%20harness%20their%20creativity.%20The%20global%20market%20for%20psychedelic%20medicine%20could%20hit%20%2410%20billion%20by%202028%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Business%20Research%20Company.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOregon%20and%20Colorado%20have%20legalized%20psilocybin%20for%20therapeutic%20use%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3Emore%20than%2020%20cities%3Cspan%3E%20have%20decriminalized%20it.%20With%20the%20hope%20that%20federal%20regulators%20will%20follow%20suit%2C%20venture%20capital%20firms%20have%20been%20financing%20shroom%20startups%2C%20and%20scores%20of%20training%20programs%20have%20sprung%20up%20to%20meet%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20psychedelic%20facilitators%20who%20can%20administer%20the%20drugs%20in%20a%20safe%20environment.%20In%20the%20San%20Francisco%20area%2C%20where%20psychedelics%20have%20a%20long%20and%20checkered%20history%2C%20at%20least%20six%20training%20programs%20now%20operate%2C%20even%20though%20psilocybin%20remains%20illegal%20for%20medicinal%20use.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERegulations%20have%20not%20changed%20with%20the%20psychedelic%20gold%20rush.%20In%20Oregon%2C%20there's%20little%20government%20or%20medical%20oversight%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpsilocybin.oregon.gov%2Ftraining-approved%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E20%20training%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20authorized%20by%20the%20state.%20Those%20certified%20to%20administer%20psychedelics%20are%20required%20to%20receive%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ecstaticintegration.org%2Fp%2Fare-new-psychedelic-guides-trained%3Fr%3D48pw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E160%20hours%20of%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%94%20compared%20with%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oregon.gov%2Fobmt%2FPages%2Flicense.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E625%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20mandated%20for%20licensed%20massage%20therapists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEAST%20%E2%80%94%20short%20for%20Entheogenic%20Assisted%20Spiritual%20Transformation%20%E2%80%94%20was%20founded%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202021.%20Located%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20of%20an%20office%20park%20in%20northwest%20Atlanta%2C%20its%20ceremonial%20space%20had%20the%20look%20of%20an%20ashram%20outfitted%20from%20an%20Anthropologie%20catalog.%20White%20sheepskin%20rugs%20were%20arranged%20in%20a%20circle%3B%20Buddhist%20statues%20adorned%20an%20altar%20lined%20with%20candles%20and%20a%20large%20geode.%20The%20veneer%20of%20curated%20calm%20was%20periodically%20pierced%20by%20the%20racket%20coming%20from%20Insight%20Virtual%20Ballistics%2C%20a%20bar%20and%20%26quot%3Bvirtual%20shooting%26quot%3B%20arcade%20next%20door.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20initial%20draw%20for%20many%20of%20the%20trainees%20at%20EAST%20was%20Franklin%2C%20who%20ran%20a%20therapy%20and%20mindfulness%20business%20in%20Atlanta%20before%20meeting%20Glattstein.%20An%20ethereal%20beauty%20with%20long%2C%20dark%20hair%20and%20a%20radiant%20smile%2C%20Franklin%20has%20an%20aesthetic%20perfectly%20suited%20to%20psychedelic%20medicine%20in%20the%20Instagram%20era.%20Her%20look%20%E2%80%94%20a%20seemingly%20endless%20rotation%20of%20hand-dyed%20silk%20dresses%20and%20turquoise%20jewelry%20%E2%80%94%20was%20at%20least%20partially%20attainable%3A%20A%20gift%20shop%20in%20EAST's%20entryway%20sold%20brightly%20hued%20dresses%20and%20robes%20for%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20a%20pop.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20Franklin%2C%2040%2C%20was%20the%20draw%2C%20it%20was%20Glattstein%2C%2065%2C%20who%20ran%20the%20show.%20He%20spent%20years%20in%20the%20up-and-down%20world%20of%20tech%20startups.%20In%201997%2C%20he%20cofounded%20an%20internet%20services%20company%20called%20Virtual%20Resources%20that%20raised%20%2425%20million%20in%20venture%20capital%2C%20only%20to%20sell%20for%20%246%20million%20two%20years%20later.%20In%202018%2C%20after%20several%20subsequent%20startups%20also%20flopped%2C%20Glattstein%20turned%20the%20page.%20Instead%20of%20pitching%20companies%2C%20he%20was%20now%20pitching%20his%20own%20rebirth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20story%2C%20as%20he's%20told%20it%20in%20various%20interviews%2C%20is%20that%20he%20had%20fallen%20terribly%20ill%20%E2%80%94%20with%20what%2C%20he%20doesn't%20say%20%E2%80%94%20and%20despite%20being%20given%20%26quot%3Ball%20of%20the%20Western%20medical%20treatments%2C%20all%20the%20therapies%2C%20all%20the%20drugs%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20mysterious%20condition%20only%20got%20worse.%20%26quot%3BThey%20had%20given%20me%20three%20months%20to%20live%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recounted%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BPsychedelic%20Conversations%26quot%3B%20podcast.%20%26quot%3BAll%20my%20systems%20were%20shutting%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20that%20changed%2C%20he%20said%2C%20when%20he%20heard%20a%20voice%20command%20him%2C%20%26quot%3BHeal%20yourself.%26quot%3B%20Glattstein%20says%20he%20stopped%20his%20medications%2C%20cut%20ties%20with%20his%20doctors%2C%20and%20started%20practicing%20with%20a%20shaman.%20His%20hair%20grew%20back%20and%20his%20body%20grew%20fit%3A%20His%20illness%20was%20gone.%20He%20started%20teaching%2C%20and%20Franklin%20was%20one%20of%20his%20early%20students.%20The%20two%20became%20a%20couple%2C%20bound%20by%20a%20passion%20for%20Eastern%20medicine%20and%2C%20they've%20said%2C%20their%20shared%20feeling%20as%20outsiders%20in%20Atlanta%20%E2%80%94%20Glattstein%2C%20the%20child%20of%20New%20York%20Jews%20in%20a%20predominantly%20Southern%20Baptist%20area%3B%20Franklin%2C%20whose%20mother%20was%20Vietnamese.%20They%20soon%20began%20hosting%20mini%20%26quot%3Bmedicine%26quot%3B%20retreats%20with%20friends%20at%20a%20cabin%20in%20the%20woods%20outside%20Atlanta.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20just%20a%20small%20group%20of%20us%20doing%20mushrooms%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20friend%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20for%20fear%20of%20professional%20repercussions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20founding%20EAST%2C%20Glattstein%20and%20Franklin%20proved%20to%20be%20gifted%20promoters%20of%20their%20new%20venture.%20Latching%20on%20to%20reality%20TV%20as%20a%20pulpit%20for%20their%20psychedelic%20gospel%2C%20they%20appeared%20as%20spiritual%20healers%20on%20Lifetime's%20%26quot%3BLittle%20Women%3A%20Atlanta%26quot%3B%20and%20Bravo's%20%26quot%3BReal%20Housewives%20of%20Atlanta%26quot%3B%20spinoff%2C%20%26quot%3BPorsha's%20Family%20Matters.%26quot%3B%20They%20trademarked%20the%20%26quot%3BEAST%20Method%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20they%20said%20provided%20%26quot%3Bprofound%20healing%20benefits%20for%20depression%2C%20anxiety%2C%20PTSD%2C%20addiction%2C%20compulsive%20conditions%2C%20pain%20management%2C%20and%20end-of-life%20demoralization%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20though%20it's%20never%20been%20proven%20to%20be%20a%20treatment%20for%20any%20condition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20they%20welcomed%20their%20first%20%26quot%3Bcouncil%26quot%3B%20of%20facilitator%20trainees%2C%20Glattstein%20%E2%80%94%20now%20calling%20himself%20a%20%26quot%3Bworld-renowned%20shaman%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20took%20on%20the%20roles%20of%20teaching%20classes%2C%20sourcing%20the%20medicine%2C%20and%20setting%20the%20dos%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20long%2C%20Glattstein%20was%20surrounded%20by%20a%20following%20of%20true%20believers.%20His%20supreme%20self-confidence%2C%20Beth%20says%2C%20made%20it%20hard%20to%20resist%20his%20instructions.%20%26quot%3BThere%20were%20moments%20where%20I%20did%20feel%20connected%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20of%20the%20drugs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20ceremony%20weekends%20at%20EAST%2C%20Friday%20and%20Saturday%20nights%20were%20reserved%20for%20psilocybin%20%26quot%3Bjourneys.%26quot%3B%20On%20the%20first%20night%2C%20half%20of%20the%20council%20would%20take%20a%20high%20dose%20of%20mushrooms%20of%20up%20to%204.5%20grams%2C%20according%20to%20six%20of%20the%20trainees.%20The%20other%20half%20would%20be%20given%20a%20relatively%20low%20dose%2C%20up%20to%201.5%20grams%2C%20so%20they%20could%20help%20facilitate%20the%20others'%20experiences%2C%20they%20say.%20Franklin%20says%20that%20the%20doses%20were%20lower%3A%203.5%20grams%20%26quot%3Bwas%20at%20a%20much%20higher%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20while%20the%20low%20dose%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bup%20to%20one%20gram.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20next%20night%2C%20they'd%20swap%20roles.%20As%20the%20students%20waited%20for%20the%20drugs%20to%20take%20effect%2C%20Franklin%20and%20the%20other%20lead%20facilitators%20would%20don%20dresses%20and%20ceremonial%20robes%2C%20play%20music%2C%20and%20dance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20the%20trainees%20would%20talk%20about%20their%20experiences%20from%20the%20night%20before.%20Glattstein%20would%20also%20lead%20sessions%20on%20topics%20like%20neuroscience%20and%20shamanic%20healing.%20The%20trainees%2C%20some%20of%20them%20healthcare%20professionals%2C%20said%20they%20found%20the%20lectures%20light%20on%20science.%20%26quot%3BJeff%20gave%20some%20very%20basic%20information%20about%20the%20limbic%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20recalls%20Sarah%2C%20a%20trainee%20in%20the%20third%20council.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20'Are%20we%20not%20going%20to%20get%20into%20serotonin%20receptors%20and%20how%20psychedelics%20interact%20with%20the%20brain%3F'%26quot%3B%20There%20was%20also%20no%20discussion%20about%20the%20boundaries%20between%20the%20facilitator%20and%20the%20subject%2C%20trainees%20say.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20never%20anything%20about%20ethics%2C%20or%20what%20we%20should%20do%20as%20facilitators%20if%20we%20found%20ourselves%20attracted%20to%20somebody%20who%20was%20doing%20the%20medicine%20work%20with%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Beth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20psychedelics%20move%20into%20the%20fields%20of%20medicine%20and%20therapy%2C%20the%20training%20in%20how%20to%20handle%20them%20is%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20being%20conducted%20by%20spiritual%20healers%20who%20are%20intensely%20critical%20of%20Western%20medicine.%20Trainees%20say%20Glattstein%20could%20be%20openly%20hostile%20to%20the%20medical%20establishment.%20Zoe%2C%20a%20former%20employee%20of%20EAST%2C%20says%20she%20started%20to%20see%20a%20shift%20in%20the%20center's%20attitude%20that%20she%20wasn't%20comfortable%20with.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20messaging%20was%20becoming%20increasingly%2C%20explicitly%20anti-mental-health%20treatment%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BLike%2C%20how%20you%20shouldn't%20go%20to%20therapy%2C%20and%20take%20mushrooms%20instead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20one%20ceremony%20in%20February%202023%2C%20a%20psychologist%20named%20Joan%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20Tim's%20council%2C%20was%20experiencing%20what%20she%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bserious%20insomnia%20and%20unrelenting%20anxiety.%26quot%3B%20She%20says%20she%20asked%20Glattstein%20if%20she%20could%20skip%20the%20mushrooms%20that%20weekend%20and%20stick%20to%20facilitating.%20But%20Joan%20says%20Glattstein%20insisted%20she%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20ceremony%20as%20planned%2C%20and%20she%20ultimately%20agreed.%20Two%20trainees%20recalled%20the%20interaction%20and%20say%20they%20wish%20they'd%20spoken%20up%20for%20Joan%20at%20the%20time.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20always%20regret%20not%20saying%2C%20'Wait%20a%20minute%2C%20Jeff%2C%20she's%20telling%20you%20that%20her%20intuition%2C%20her%20body%2C%20her%20spirit%2C%20is%20saying%20that%20she%20shouldn't%20do%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Beth.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20would%20we%20override%20that%3F%20We're%20here%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20be%20facilitators.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFranklin%20says%20she%20knew%20Joan%20was%20struggling%2C%20but%20denies%20Glattstein%20pressured%20her%20to%20take%20mushrooms.%20As%20the%20course%20progressed%2C%20Joan's%20symptoms%20got%20worse.%20By%20the%20time%20it%20was%20over%2C%20she%20was%20a%20wreck.%20%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20sleep.%20I%20couldn't%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20stopped%20doing%20pretty%20much%20anything.%26quot%3B%20Her%20husband%20admitted%20her%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20and%20she%20remained%20in%20the%20psych%20ward%20for%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20same%20weekend%20that%20Joan%20asked%20to%20skip%20the%20mushrooms%2C%20Tim%20also%20tried%20to%20scale%20back%20his%20dosage%20after%20his%20bad%20breakup.%20Ahead%20of%20the%20ceremony%2C%20he%20says%20he%20went%20to%20two%20of%20EAST's%20employees%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20was%20Scott%2C%20and%20told%20them%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20may%20not%20be%20appropriate%20for%20me%20to%20take%20a%20high%20dose%20of%20psilocybin%20this%20weekend.%26quot%3B%20When%20Glattstein%20proceeded%20as%20normal%2C%20Tim%20agreed%20to%20take%20the%20high%20dose.%20He%20remembers%20his%20trip%20that%20night%20as%20healing%2C%20helping%20him%20to%20view%20the%20breakup%20as%20%26quot%3Bjust%20a%20blip%20in%20our%20cosmic%20story.%26quot%3B%20He%20was%20filled%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20%26quot%3Boverwhelming%20love%26quot%3B%20for%20his%20ex%2C%20and%20was%20certain%20they%20would%20meet%20again%20in%20future%20lives.%20As%20the%20ceremony%20wound%20down%2C%20Tim%20was%20still%20tripping.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrainees%20say%20this%20was%20a%20common%20issue%20at%20EAST.%20The%20medicine%20ceremonies%20ended%20after%20three%20hours%2C%20and%20the%20effects%20of%20a%20high%20dose%20of%20psilocybin%20might%20last%20up%20to%20eight%20hours.%20It%20took%20so%20long%20to%20come%20down%20that%20trainees%20would%20make%20arrangements%20for%20someone%20to%20drive%20them%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223750%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20figure%20experiencing%20a%20trip%20while%20an%20anonymous%20figure%20is%20touching%20them%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6824ae613fe8d3928365cffc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETim%20came%20to%20believe%20that%20EAST%20had%20taken%20his%20money%20and%20put%20him%20in%20the%20care%20of%20someone%20who%20took%20advantage%20of%20him%20while%20he%20was%20in%20a%20suggestible%20state.%3Cp%3EDeena%20So%20Oteh%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETim%20and%20Scott%20knew%20each%20other%20from%20years%20earlier%2C%20when%20they'd%20gone%20on%20a%20few%20dates%2C%20but%20both%20say%20it%20never%20turned%20sexual.%20That%20night%2C%20Scott%20was%20already%20due%20to%20give%20Tim%20a%20ride%20home%20from%20the%20ceremony%2C%20along%20with%20another%20trainee%20who%20was%20staying%20at%20Scott's%20home%20that%20weekend.%20Now%2C%20Tim%20says%20that%20Scott%20suggested%20Tim%20stay%20over%2C%20too.%20Wouldn't%20that%20be%20better%2C%20he%20said%2C%20than%20returning%20to%20the%20home%20Tim%20shared%20with%20his%20ex-boyfriend%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EOh%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Tim%20thought%20as%20he%20stared%20out%20the%20window%2C%20gazing%20at%20the%20passing%20lights%20amplified%20by%20the%20psilocybin.%20%3Cem%3EHow%20lovely%20that%20this%20person%20would%20offer%20me%20a%20place%20to%20sleep.%20%3C%2Fem%3EAfter%20several%20months%20of%20psilocybin%20use%2C%20he%20felt%20a%20deep%20affection%20for%20everyone%20involved%20with%20EAST%2C%20including%20Scott.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20other%20trainee%20would%20be%20staying%20on%20the%20couch%2C%20Tim%20says%20Scott%20suggested%20that%20they%20could%20share%20his%20bed.%20(The%20other%20trainee%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.)%20Still%20feeling%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20psilocybin%2C%20Tim%20agreed.%20But%20as%20Scott%20crawled%20into%20bed%20with%20him%2C%20the%20feeling%20of%20love%20and%20connection%20Tim%20had%20felt%20on%20the%20ride%20home%20dissolved%20into%20confusion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20%26quot%3Bkind%20of%20turned%20into%20this%20archetype%20of%20a%20tiger%2C%26quot%3B%20Tim%20recalls%2C%20%26quot%3Bwith%20the%20growling%20and%20these%20half-closed%20eyes.%26quot%3B%20As%20Tim%20recalls%20it%2C%20Scott%20tried%20to%20undress%20him%20and%20physically%20force%20him%20to%20perform%20oral%20sex.%20%26quot%3BI%20put%20my%20underwear%20back%20on%20at%20least%20three%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20Tim%20says.%20Finally%2C%20Tim%20says%20he%20gave%20up%20trying%20to%20resist.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20telephone%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Scott%20denied%20having%20%26quot%3Bany%20sexual%20contact%26quot%3B%20with%20Tim.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Tim%2C%20they%20wound%20up%20having%20one%20more%20sexual%20encounter%20with%20another%20man%2C%20though%20Scott%20says%20he%20was%20present%20but%20didn't%20participate.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20reviewed%20text%20messages%20between%20Tim%20and%20Scott%2C%20in%20which%20they%20exchanged%20friendly%20banter%20and%2C%20on%20one%20occasion%2C%20Scott%20sent%20Tim%20an%20explicit%20photo.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20months%20after%20the%20alleged%20assault%2C%20and%20after%20Tim%20had%20opened%20up%20to%20his%20therapist%2C%20Tim%20says%20he%20came%20to%20believe%20that%20EAST%20had%20taken%20his%20money%20and%20put%20him%20in%20the%20care%20of%20someone%20who%20took%20advantage%20of%20him%20while%20he%20was%20in%20a%20suggestible%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20retrospect%2C%20he%20puts%20much%20of%20the%20blame%20for%20what%20happened%20on%20Glattstein%20and%20Franklin.%20After%20all%2C%20they%20were%20the%20ones%20who%20put%20Scott%20in%20charge%20of%20getting%20him%20home%20safely.%20%26quot%3BHow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20began%20to%20wonder%2C%20%26quot%3Bare%20these%20people%20running%20a%20training%20program%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20lack%20of%20clear%20guidelines%20is%20a%20widespread%20problem%20in%20facilitator%20training.%20The%20gold%20standard%20for%20centers%20like%20EAST%20is%20a%20manual%20developed%20by%20the%20Multidisciplinary%20Association%20for%20Psychedelic%20Studies%2C%20the%20country's%20leading%20psychedelic%20and%20research%20advocacy%20organization.%20But%20the%20guidelines%20provided%20by%20MAPS%20are%20murky%20at%20best.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20manual%20states%20that%20facilitators%20must%20%26quot%3Balways%20ask%20for%20permission%20regarding%20any%20kind%20of%20physical%20contact.%26quot%3B%20The%20guidelines%20don't%20address%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20person%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20psychedelics%20may%20not%20be%20in%20a%20position%20to%20consent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuggesting%20physical%20contact%20with%20someone%20who%20is%20on%20psychedelic%20drugs%2C%20by%20its%20very%20nature%2C%20fosters%20an%20environment%20that%20is%20ripe%20for%20abuse.%20%26quot%3BIt%20goes%20against%20everything%20we%20know%20about%20therapeutic%20boundaries%20and%20ethics%20when%20the%20facilitator%20or%20therapist%20leans%20heavily%20into%20touch%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Ne%C5%9Fe%20Devenot%2C%20a%20researcher%20at%20the%20Project%20on%20Psychedelics%20Law%20and%20Regulation%20at%20Harvard.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20when%20the%20client%20is%20on%20these%20suggestible%20substances%2C%20that%20touch%20creates%20a%20feeling%20of%20intimacy%20that%20can%20be%20exploited.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBetty%20Aldworth%2C%20the%20director%20of%20communications%20and%20education%20at%20MAPS%2C%20said%20the%20organization's%20guidelines%20are%20clear.%20She%20says%20the%20MAPS%20manual%20stresses%20that%20touch%20is%20optional%20and%20that%20consent%20for%20touch%20can%20be%20revoked%20at%20any%20time%20and%20in%20different%20ways%2C%20including%20nonverbally.%20She%20added%20that%20proper%20training%20and%20sound%20clinical%20judgment%20are%20crucial%20to%20the%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202019%2C%20MAPS%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmaps.org%2F2019%2F05%2F24%2Fstatement-public-announcement-of-ethical-violation-by-former-maps-sponsored-investigators%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacknowledged%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20Richard%20Yensen%2C%20an%20unlicensed%20therapist%20in%20one%20of%20its%20clinical%20trials%2C%20%26quot%3Bsubstantially%20deviated%26quot%3B%20from%20its%20manual%20while%20treating%20Meaghan%20Buisson%2C%20a%20trial%20participant%20who%20suffered%20from%20post-traumatic%20stress%20disorder%20stemming%20in%20part%20from%20sexual%20abuse.%20Video%20footage%20of%20the%20treatment%20showed%20Yensen%20and%20another%20therapist%20cuddling%2C%20hugging%2C%20and%20aggressively%20restraining%20Buisson%20while%20she%20was%20on%20MDMA.%20In%20a%20lawsuit%2C%20Buisson%20alleges%20that%20following%20the%20treatment%2C%20Yensen%20continued%20to%20act%20as%20her%20therapist%20and%20repeatedly%20sexually%20abused%20her%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%20after%20the%20initial%20incident.%20After%20Buisson%20sued%20him%20for%20sexual%20abuse%2C%20Yensen%20argued%20in%20a%20legal%20filing%20that%20the%20relationship%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcms.qz.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F4-Yensen-court-response.pdf%3F_gl%3D1*4ge3p7*_ga*MTI4NjMxNDg2OS4xNzIzNDI1MTMw*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTcyMzQ2NzQ3MC4yLjAuMTcyMzQ2NzQ3MC42MC4wLjA.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsensual%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%2C%20because%20his%20therapy%20license%20had%20lapsed%2C%20he%20was%20not%20under%20a%20%26quot%3Bduty%20of%20care%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20medical%20professional.%20The%20case%20was%20settled%20out%20of%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202022%2C%20California's%20Board%20of%20Behavioral%20Science%20brought%20eight%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsearch.dca.ca.gov%2Fdownloadd0022f2a848132072353c15edbad3c5ba28f5c9c78401277e596b80b4e8763c1f4a8bbc5faded43a23ec5762d81f88e05455ae668c9e69a10a6597a7dcc57b8612bb59e7e66da42ac3a8b5923a11a7367d1d0110d5f5f8e435e3a55e2144c2f151fc75f69e8dcc36656bdc7bb7a8fbd5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecauses%20for%20discipline%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3B%20against%20Eyal%20Goren%2C%20a%20therapist%20who%20trained%20with%20the%20Center%20for%20Consciousness%20Medicine.%20The%20claims%20included%20sexual%20misconduct%2C%20gross%20negligence%2C%20and%20emotional%20harm%20against%20trainees%20who%20had%20taken%20psilocybin%2C%20MDMA%2C%20and%20ayahuasca.%20Goren%20denied%20the%20allegations%2C%20but%20agreed%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsearch.dca.ca.gov%2Fdownloadd0022f2a848132072353c15edbad3c5b03d6845842d435a4457c0b4a47ca22cfbb3741072628f9967eaae554af254b7003b05a5b026eec53293305daa6ddc13e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurrender%20his%20license%20for%20at%20least%20three%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Goren%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202021%2C%20200%20psychedelic%20practitioners%20and%20advocates%20signed%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpsychedeliccommunity.medium.com%2Faddressing-abuse-and-repair-an-open-letter-to-the-psychedelic-community-ccf677dd92b9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopen%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20calling%20for%20accountability%20and%20transparency%20in%20the%20psychedelic%20community.%20A%20healthcare%20blog%20published%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.petrieflom.law.harvard.edu%2F2024%2F03%2F01%2Fbioethics-psychedelic-therapy-abuse-and-the-risk-of-ethics-washing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarvard%20Law%20School%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20co-authored%20by%20Devenot%2C%20concluded%20that%20the%20accounts%20of%20abuse%20throughout%20the%20rapidly%20growing%20ecosystem%20of%20psychedelic%20medicine%20%26quot%3Balign%20with%20the%20familiar%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psychiatrictimes.com%2Fview%2Fresponding-to-authoritarian-cults-and-extreme-exploitations-a-new-framework-to-evaluate-undue-influence%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20dynamics%20that%20make%20up%20destructive%20cults%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFranklin%20says%20EAST%20did%20consider%20ethics%20when%20setting%20up%20the%20program%2C%20but%20she%20concedes%20they%20could%20have%20done%20more.%20%26quot%3BEAST%20was%20not%20perfect%2C%20obviously%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20growth%20area%20for%20sure%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20definitely%20did%20our%20best.%26quot%3B%20Still%2C%20she%20adds%2C%20the%20institute%20can't%20be%20blamed%20for%20what%20happened%20outside%20its%20training.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20people%20did%20when%20they%20stepped%20outside%20of%20the%20doors%2C%20we%20just%20don't%20have%20control%20over%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMembers%20of%20Tim's%20council%20were%20shell-shocked%20by%20his%20allegations.%20As%20they%20debated%20what%20to%20do%2C%20more%20allegations%20surfaced%20%E2%80%94%20this%20time%20about%20Glattstein.%20In%20October%202023%2C%20two%20women%20from%20EAST's%20first%20facilitator%20training%20sued%20Glattstein%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20had%20sexually%20abused%20them%20during%20private%20%26quot%3Benergy%20healing%26quot%3B%20sessions.%20One%20of%20the%20women%2C%20Mica%20Davis%2C%20said%20Glattstein%20would%20touch%20her%20breasts%20and%20vagina%20over%20her%20clothing%2C%20ostensibly%20to%20help%20clear%20her%20%26quot%3Broot%20chakra%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20energy%20that%20resides%20in%20the%20groin%20area.%20Doing%20so%2C%20he%20told%20her%2C%20would%20%26quot%3Bmake%20her%20husband%20happy.%26quot%3B%20The%20second%20woman%2C%20Jacqueline%20Wigder%2C%20who%20had%20come%20to%20EAST%20in%20part%20to%20work%20through%20trauma%20stemming%20from%20childhood%20sexual%20abuse%2C%20said%20that%20Glattstein%20would%20press%20his%20hands%20on%20her%20pubic%20bone%20and%20reach%20under%20her%20bra%20to%20run%20his%20hands%20between%20her%20breasts.%20Her%20sexual%20energy%2C%20he%20allegedly%20told%20her%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Blike%20a%20caged%20tiger%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20released.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGlattstein%20and%20EAST%20have%20denied%20the%20allegations.%20In%20a%20blog%20post%20on%20his%20personal%20website%2C%20Glattstein%20says%20the%20women%20signed%20informed%20consents%20specifically%20for%20%26quot%3Bhands%20on%26quot%3B%20energy%20work.%20%26quot%3BThe%20reputation%20of%20an%20incredibly%20gifted%20healer%20that%20has%20dedicated%20his%20life%20to%20helping%20humanity%20was%20severely%20damaged%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20The%20case%20is%20still%20pending.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20December%2C%20EAST%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy.%20The%20EAST%20website%20is%20now%20blank%2C%20and%20all%20posts%20have%20been%20deleted%20from%20the%20group's%20social%20media%20accounts.%20Franklin%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20migrated%20some%20of%20EAST's%20offerings%20to%20her%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lenafranklin.com%2Fexpand-peru-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonal%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20she%20offered%20a%20six-day%20trip%20to%20Egypt%20called%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDBG7lRYue43%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link%26igsh%3DMzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Awakening%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20she%20advertised%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Breclamation%20journey%20of%20the%20powerful%20Priestess%20within%26quot%3B%20that%20will%20unlock%20%26quot%3Bdormant%20cellular%20DNA.%26quot%3B%20Today%2C%20she%20says%2C%20her%20goal%20is%20%26quot%3Bto%20share%20what%20it%20really%20means%20to%20be%20an%20impactful%2C%20courageous%2C%20conscious%20leader%20in%20the%20healing%20and%20psychedelic%20spaces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20Tim%2C%20he%20hopes%20for%20a%20day%20when%20psilocybin%20therapy%20is%20fully%20professionalized%2C%20with%20credentials%20and%20oversight%20boards.%20In%20a%20sense%2C%20it's%20n