aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20is%20relying%20on%20the%20profits%20from%20their%20future%20home%20sale%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-boomer-homeowners-cashed-in-downsized-retirement-home-equity-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20fund%20their%20retirement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Friedman%20is%20concerned%20that%20his%20Social%20Security%20checks%20and%20his%20wife's%20pension%20won't%20be%20enough%20to%20cover%20healthcare%20bills%20and%20long-term%20care%20as%20they%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20among%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20potential%20home%20sellers%20facing%20a%20hefty%20tax%20that's%20discouraging%20them%20from%20parting%20with%20their%20valuable%20properties.%20This%20has%20likely%20helped%20exacerbate%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-boomers-wont-sell-homes-millennials-kids-need-housing-affordability-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshortage%20of%20family-sized%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20market.%20Many%20of%20those%20affected%20are%20older%20people%20who%20are%20looking%20to%20downsize%20but%20are%20relying%20on%20their%20homes%20to%20be%20their%20retirement%20nest%20eggs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20may%20be%20relief%20on%20the%20horizon%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20a%20bipartisan%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20recently%20said%20he's%20considering%20entirely%20eliminating%20the%20capital%20gains%20tax%20on%20home%20sales%20to%20help%20juice%20the%20housing%20market%20amid%20persistently%20high%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Fed%20would%20lower%20the%20rates%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20even%20have%20to%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20told%20reporters%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20on%20July%2022.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20are%20thinking%20about%20no%20tax%20on%20capital%20gains%20on%20houses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20desperate%20to%20move%2C%20the%20Friedmans%20finally%20put%20their%20house%20on%20the%20market%20in%20May%20for%20nearly%20%244.5%20million.%20But%20now%20that%20Trump%20and%20members%20of%20Congress%20are%20talking%20about%20eliminating%20the%20tax%2C%20they're%20letting%20their%20listing%20expire%20and%20hoping%20the%20law%20changes%20before%20they%20put%20it%20back%20up%20for%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20you%20an%20older%20American%20who%20has%20struggled%20to%20downsize%20your%20home%20or%20find%20retirement%20housing%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aerelman%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eerelman%40businessinsider.com.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2215d17c0c-cf15-4af2-bd2f-5408e7618f12%5C%22%3ESafe-guarding%20their%20nest%20egg%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20part%20because%20home%20prices%20have%20soared%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20share%20of%20home%20sales%20subject%20to%20the%20tax%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2034%25%20of%20America's%20homeowners%20%E2%80%94%C2%A029%20million%20people%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0could%20exceed%20the%20%24250%2C000%20cap%20for%20single%20filers%20if%20they%20were%20to%20sell%2C%20and%2010%25%20could%20exceed%20the%20%24500%2C000%20threshold%2C%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Realtors%20found%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nar.realtor%2Fadvocacy%2Ffederal-advocacy%2Fnar-legislative-priorities%23capital%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%202025%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%202023%2C%208%25%20of%20US%20sellers%20made%20more%20than%20%24500%2C000%20in%20profit%20on%20the%20sale%20of%20their%20homes%2C%20the%20property%20data%20firm%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.corelogic.com%2Fintelligence%2Funexpected-surprise-more-homeowners-paying-capital-gains-taxes-strong-price-growth%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECoreLogic%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20found.%20That's%20up%20from%201.3%25%20in%202003%20and%203%25%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20threshold%20had%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bls.gov%2Fdata%2Finflation_calculator.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eadjusted%20for%20inflation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20it%20was%20implemented%2C%20the%20%24250%2C000%20cutoff%20for%20individual%20home%20sellers%20in%201997%20dollars%20would%20be%20about%20twice%20as%20high%20%E2%80%94%20%24496%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20in%202024%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20housing%20economists%20believe%20that%20increasing%20the%20threshold%20for%20the%20tax%20or%20eliminating%20the%20levy%20altogether%20could%20boost%20crucial%20housing%20inventory%20by%20incentivizing%20homeowners%20to%20sell.%20But%20others%20are%20skeptical%20that%20it%20would%20make%20much%20of%20a%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20doesn't%20necessarily%20lead%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20inventory%3B%20it%20just%20leads%20to%20a%20turnover%20in%20the%20housing%20market%2C%20more%20home%20sale%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20particularly%20in%20expensive%20markets%20in%20places%20like%20California%20and%20New%20York%2C%20said%20Selma%20Hepp%2C%20the%20chief%20economist%20at%20CoreLogic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20real-estate%20company%20Redfin%20reported%20that%20as%20of%202022%2C%20empty-nest%20boomers%20owned%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-boomers-wont-sell-homes-millennials-kids-need-housing-affordability-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etwice%20as%20many%20homes%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20three%20or%20more%20bedrooms%20as%20millennials%20with%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMary%20Ellen%20Taylor%2C%2075%2C%20is%20one%20of%20those%20homeowners.%20She%20and%20her%20husband%20would%20like%20to%20downsize%20from%20their%20six-bedroom%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20home%2C%20but%20they're%20staying%20put%20in%20part%20because%20of%20the%20capital%20gains%20tax.%20Taylor%2C%20who%20worked%20for%20decades%20in%20housing%20finance%20regulation%2C%20argued%20that%20the%20policy%20incentivizes%20boomers%20like%20herself%20to%20hold%20onto%20their%20large%20homes%2C%20when%20they%20should%20be%20selling%20them%20to%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20all%20the%20fuss%20that%20is%20made%2C%20rightly%20so%2C%20about%20the%20supply%20of%20housing%2C%20having%20tax%20incentives%20that%20run%20completely%20counter%20to%20what%20your%20public%20policy%20aims%20of%20increasing%20the%20supply%20of%20housing%20is%20silly%2C%26quot%3B%20Taylor%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20you%20want%20a%20bunch%20of%2075-year-olds%20occupying%20six-bedroom%20houses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2228ab624f-da50-461f-a930-7a578f60b2fc%5C%22%3EA%20bipartisan%20issue%20with%20complicated%20impacts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20weeks%20before%20the%20president%20floated%20eliminating%20the%20tax%20on%20home%20sales%2C%20Republican%20Rep.%20Marjorie%20Taylor%20Greene%20introduced%20legislation%20seeking%20to%20do%20just%20that.%20Greene%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FRepMTG%2Fstatus%2F1947693719706079332%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecelebrated%3C%2Fa%3E%20Trump's%20comments%20as%20an%20endorsement%20of%20her%20No%20Tax%20on%20Home%20Sales%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20Democratic%20support%20for%20reforming%20the%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERep.%20Jimmy%20Panetta%2C%20a%20California%20Democrat%20whose%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpanetta.house.gov%2Fabout%2Four-district%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edistrict%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20includes%20several%20pricey%20coastal%20regions%2C%20first%20introduced%20a%20bill%20in%202022%20that%20would%20double%20the%20tax%20exclusion%20to%20%24500%2C000%20for%20individuals%20and%20%241%20million%20for%20joint-filing%20couples%20and%20index%20it%20to%20inflation.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkelly.house.gov%2Fmedia%2Fpress-releases%2Freps-kelly-panetta-reintroduce-bipartisan-legislation-make-housing-more%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMore%20Homes%20on%20the%20Market%20Act%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20has%20cosponsors%20across%20the%20aisle%2C%20aims%20to%20incentivize%20more%20homeowners%20to%20sell%20and%20boost%20housing%20inventory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPanetta%20said%20he's%20willing%20to%20work%20with%20Trump%20and%20Republicans%20on%20%26quot%3Ba%20quick%20and%20rewarding%20way%20to%20incentivize%20people%20to%20sell%20their%20homes%20and%20keep%20intact%20their%20nest%20egg.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20hope%20that%20the%20President%20is%20serious%20about%20doing%20something%2C%20and%20not%20just%20saying%20it%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20a%20fix%20for%20the%20affordable%20housing%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20any%20major%20policy%20change%2C%20there%20could%20be%20big%20unintended%20consequences%20down%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHepp%20warned%20that%20sellers%20who%20walk%20away%20with%20extra%20cash%20in%20hand%20would%20then%20have%20more%20money%20to%20spend%20on%20their%20next%20home%2C%20which%20could%20put%20upward%20pressure%20on%20home%20prices.%20In%20a%20CNBC%20interview%2C%20Redfin%20chief%20economist%20Daryl%20Fairweather%20argued%20that%20changing%20the%20tax%20could%20perversely%20incentivize%20some%20homeowners%20who'd%20been%20planning%20to%20sell%20before%20reaching%20the%20current%20tax%20threshold%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Fvideo%2F2025%2F07%2F22%2Fnot-clear-ending-capital-gains-tax-on-homes-would-help-housing-market-says-redfins-fairweather.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20hold%20onto%20their%20homes%20for%20longer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20the%20tax%20break%20stimulates%20home%20sales%2C%20it%20won't%20address%20the%20fundamental%20shortage%20of%20housing%20across%20the%20country.%20Older%20homeowners%20who%20finally%20sell%20their%20homes%20and%20move%20still%20need%20to%20live%20somewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20still%20stuck%20with%20this%20problem%20of%20lack%20of%20housing%20in%20the%20US%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20the%20problem%20that%20should%20be%20tackled.%20How%20do%20we%20build%20more%2C%20less%20expensively%20and%20more%20quickly%3F%26quot%3B%20Hepp%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReducing%20the%20capital%20gains%20burden%20would%20also%20disproportionately%20benefit%20higher-income%20Americans%2C%20even%20as%20many%20of%20these%20same%20households%20receive%20other%20forms%20of%20tax%20relief%20under%20Trump's%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-big-beautiful-bill-medicaid-taxes-maga-accounts-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eone%20big%20beautiful%20bill%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20As%20part%20of%20that%20law%2C%20many%20wealthy%20homeowners%20in%20high-tax%20states%20will%20benefit%20from%20an%20increase%20to%20the%20cap%20on%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-trump-big-beautiful-bill-impacts-wallet-taxes-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20state%20and%20local%20tax%20deduction%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEliminating%20the%20tax%20on%20home%20sales%20would%20also%20cost%20the%20federal%20government%20in%20lost%20revenue%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Republicans%20are%20adding%20at%20least%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvenmo-national-debt-payment-treasury-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%243.4%20trillion%20to%20the%20national%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20her%20support%20for%20reform%2C%20Taylor%20believes%20the%20tax%20code%20is%20%26quot%3Bwildly%20to%20the%20benefit%20of%20more%20affluent%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20worries%20that%20eliminating%20the%20capital%20gains%20tax%20could%20further%20skew%20the%20US%20tax%20code%20in%20favor%20of%20wealthier%