ear.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6ebc54a-547c-40e7-866e-e4380856a99e%5C%22%3EI%20don't%20have%20an%20endpoint%20in%20mind%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20also%20ask%20me%20how%20to%20do%20this%20type%20of%20ban%20if%20there%20are%20weight%20changes.%20I've%20had%20a%2040-pound%20weight%20swing%2C%20needing%20new-to-me%20clothing%20to%20fit%20my%20changing%20body.%20But%20the%20different%20sizes%20aren't%20coming%20from%20a%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20considered%20breaking%20my%20ban%20a%20couple%20of%20times%2C%20thinking%20about%20what%20I%20would%20buy%2C%20but%20I%20have%20yet%20to%20think%20of%20something%20worth%20buying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20I%20needed%20black%20leggings%20%E2%80%94%20mine%20were%20very%20worn.%20Someone%20then%20put%20three%20pairs%20up%20on%20the%20Buy%20Nothing%20Facebook%20group.%20They%20weren't%20the%20exact%20size%20or%20style%20I%20would%20have%20chosen%2C%20but%20I'm%20flexible%20and%20gratefully%20accepted%20them.%20I'm%20not%20a%20woo-woo%20manifester%2C%20but%20I%20do%20think%20the%20universe%20has%20shown%20up%20when%20I%20needed%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20don't%20have%20an%20endpoint%20in%20mind%2C%20there%20may%20come%20a%20day%20when%20I%20need%20to%20buy%20new.%20It'll%20need%20to%20be%20worth%20it%2C%20and%20the%20purchase%20will%20need%20to%20either%20be%20from%20a%20thrift%20store%20or%20a%20carefully%20vetted%20company%20that%20is%20both%20sustainable%20and%20ethical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-havent-bought-any-new-clothes-in-eightyears-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753544161000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f18eac6ad288d14826344%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-havent-bought-any-new-clothes-in-eightyears-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Angela%20Rozmyn%20was%20overwhelmed%20b