ss%2C%20he%20expanded%20cultivation%20by%20another%20four%20acres%20a%20few%20years%20later.%20Today%2C%20his%20orchard%20spans%20nearly%2020%20acres%2C%20yielding%20an%20impressive%20seven%20tonnes%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FKaspate-in-his-nursery-with-a-custard-apple-sapling_11zon-1753429459-500x667.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Golden%20Sitaphal%20farmer%20innovator%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FKaspate-in-his-nursery-with-a-custard-apple-sapling_11zon-1753429459-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FKaspate-in-his-nursery-with-a-custard-apple-sapling_11zon-1753429459-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FKaspate-in-his-nursery-with-a-custard-apple-sapling_11zon-1753429459-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FKaspate-in-his-nursery-with-a-custard-apple-sapling_11zon-1753429459-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FKaspate-in-his-nursery-with-a-custard-apple-sapling_11zon-1753429459-150x200.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FKaspate-in-his-nursery-with-a-custard-apple-sapling_11zon-1753429459.jpg%201149w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-476009%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKaspate%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20grow%20grapes%20and%20ber%2C%20but%20after%20developing%20NMK-01%2C%20I%20converted%20my%20entire%20farm%20to%20Sitaphal%2C%20inspiring%20others%20to%20follow.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavi%20attributes%20his%20high%20productivity%20to%20disciplined%20crop%20management%2C%20especially%20eight%20annual%20foliar%20sprays%20that%20keep%20pests%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%202018%2C%2055-year-old%20Dinesh%20Patidar%20from%20Jamli%20village%20in%20Mhow%20Cantonment%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20planted%204%2C800%20saplings%20sourced%20from%20Madhuban%20across%2012%20acres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20grow%20a%20mix%20of%20fruits%20like%20mango%2C%20dragon%20fruit%2C%20guava%2C%20and%20avocado.%20Sitaphal%20starts%20bearing%20fruit%20in%20October%2C%20and%20the%20harvest%20continues%20through%20mid-January.%20I%20typically%20get%20four%20to%20five%20tonnes%20per%20acre%2C%20bringing%20in%20a%20profit%20of%20around%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20per%20acre%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENew%20varieties%20and%20the%20road%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaspate%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20taken%20me%20close%20to%2012%20years%20to%20develop%20the%20new%20varieties%E2%80%94NMK%20Arvi%20and%20NMK%20Samruddhi.%20Arvi%20is%20a%20cross%20between%20NMK-01%20(Golden)%20and%20Lal%20Sitaphal%2C%20while%20the%20red-coloured%20Samruddhi%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20Sitaphal%20and%20Ramphal%20(%3Cem%3EAnnona%20reticulata%3C%2Fem%3E).%20Both%20are%20harvested%20in%20February.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20December%202021%2C%20NMK%20Samruddhi%20has%20been%20tested%20over%20six%20harvests.%20On%20average%2C%20each%20fruit%20weighed%20350%20grams%2C%20had%2060%25%20pulp%2C%20and%20a%20sweetness%20level%20(Brix)%20of%2025%E2%80%94making%20it%20a%20favourite%20among%20both%20farmers%20and%20buyers.%20NMK%20Arvi%20also%20showed%20similar%20results%2C%20with%20350-gram%20fruits%2C%2055%25%20pulp%2C%20fewer%20seeds%2C%20and%20the%20same%20sweetness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaspate%20has%20distributed%20saplings%20for%20trials%20to%20farmers%20in%20Ghormale%20and%20Barshi%20talukas%20and%20plans%20to%20launch%20the%20new%20varieties%20once%20he%20secures%20IPR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20submitted%20the%20documents%20about%20the%20newly%20developed%20varieties%20to%20PPV%26amp%3BRA%20in%20November%202023.%20I%20will%20introduce%20them%20to%20farmers%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20challenge%20of%20counterfeiting%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20on%20new%20varieties%2C%20Kaspate%20continues%20to%20battle%20counterfeiters%E2%80%94a%20major%20challenge%20for%20farmer-innovators%20in%20India.%20Many%20nurseries%20sell%20unauthorised%20saplings%20under%20different%20names%20to%20hide%20their%20origin%2C%20but%20they%20are%20all%20NMK-01%20(Golden)%2C%20for%20which%20Kaspate%20holds%20the%20IPR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20filed%20cases%20in%20the%20Solapur%20District%20Court%20against%20220%20nurseries%20for%20selling%20counterfeits%20and%20has%20paid%20Rs%2015%20lakhs%20in%20stamp%20duty%20for%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20every%20breakthrough%2C%20Kaspate%20not%20only%20uplifts%20his%20community%20but%20redefines%20what%20it%20means%20to%20farm%20with%20purpose%20in%20dryland%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20images%20courtesy%20Hiren%20Bose%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753450921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FNMK-Arvi_11zon-1753429470.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D475953%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Navnath%20Kaspate%E2%80%99s%20breakthrough%20custard%20apple%20varieties%20are%20transforming%20drought-prone%20farming%2C%20doubling%20yields%2C%20and%20inspiring%20thousands.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hiren%20Kumar%20Bose%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F475953%2Ffarmer-innovator-golden-sitaphal-custard-apple-navnath-kaspate-maharashtra-madhya-pradesh%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%