tlines%20decade-wise%20roadmaps%20for%20transitioning%20across%2013%20coal-dependent%20districts.%20Chhattisgarh%20rolled%20out%20community%20energy%20initiatives%20(solar%20electrification%20in%20Bastar%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20villages)%20and%20piloted%20hydrogen%20trucking%20for%20cleaner%20mining%20operations%20at%20the%20district%20level.%20While%20these%20efforts%20are%20commendable%2C%20they%20are%20still%20limited%20to%20a%20few%20states.%20Thus%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20anchor%20state%20just%20transition%20plans%20in%20state%20energy%20policies%20and%20mandate%20the%20submission%20of%20%E2%80%98just%20transition%20roadmaps%E2%80%99%20to%20ensure%20binding%20commitments%20and%20alignment%20with%20central%20energy%20goals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Early%20reskilling%20and%20workforce%20planning%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20district-level%20workforce%20mapping%20in%20coal%20regions%2C%20including%20formal%2C%20informal%2C%20and%20dependent%20populations%2C%20should%20be%20conducted%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20workforce%20in%20the%20coal%20sector%20is%20not%20affected%20by%20the%20transition.%20The%20targeted%20reskilling%20for%20jobs%20in%20solar%2C%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs)%2C%20energy%20efficiency%2C%20and%20green%20hydrogen%20should%20be%20initiated%20at%20least%202%E2%80%933%20years%20before%20the%20projected%20mine%20or%20plant%20decommissioning%2C%20using%20the%20Skill%20Council%20for%20Green%20Jobs%20(SCGJ)%E2%80%93aligned%20curriculum.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753409739.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Reskilling%20coal%20sector%20workers%20for%20solar%2C%20EVs%2C%20and%20green%20hydrogen%20is%20key%20to%20a%20just%20transition.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.