%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-24T121623.275-1753339597-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-24T121623.275-1753339597-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-475420%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20local%20of%20Shillong%20who%20delegated%20the%20work%20of%20making%20a%20dog%20house%20to%20Green%20Ammo.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20excitement%20is%20palpable%2C%20especially%20among%20children%20who%20have%20never%20before%20felt%20their%20voices%20or%20actions%20mattered.%20%E2%80%9COne%20girl%20came%20to%20me%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Didi%2C%20I%20never%20thought%20I%20could%20build%20something.%20But%20I%20made%20this%20brick%2C%20and%20now%20it%E2%80%99s%20part%20of%20our%20toilet%2C%E2%80%9D%20Momo%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20the%20magic%20happens.%20When%20a%20child%20sees%20that%20their%20waste%2C%20something%20they%20thought%20had%20no%20value%2C%20can%20become%20a%20school%20bench%20or%20a%20wall%2C%20they%20understand%20the%20power%20of%20action.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESukanta%20sums%20it%20up%20best%3A%20%E2%80%9CProjects%20like%20this%20give%20something%20back%20to%20students%20that%20they%20can%20relate%20to.%20It%20becomes%20part%20of%20their%20identity%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20happy%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20not%20just%20lessons%20in%20recycling%3B%20they%20are%20life%20lessons%20in%20agency%2C%20empathy%2C%20and%20empowerment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENature%20is%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20responsibility%2C%20and%20change%20begins%20with%20shared%20ownership%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20sceptics%20who%20question%20whether%20plastic%20can%20be%20used%20to%20build%20safe%20infrastructure%2C%20Amit%20is%20clear%3A%